      <Content>One may also classify the meaning of μελος in Domain 63 Whole, Unite, Part, Divide and consider its reference to body parts as only an instance of an even more generic meaning, namely, part ({D:63.17}). On the other hand, its frequent association wit the body in absolute contexts may justify its classification here as a generic for body parts.</Content>
